name: The Great Horned Owl - Lavender
description:
Nocturnal Pastel - Lavender 
Shedding light on creatures that play in the dark. 

“Belonging to the magic of the night, darkness is no obstacle for the nocturnal Great Horned Owl. It is said that the owl is the wisest of all birds because the more it sees the less it talks.”

Visit original edit in the neenTAE collection on opensea. (Part 1 of Nocturnal Buttone)
